The paper discusses the application of deep learning and neural network models in intrusion detection systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses various methodologies related to deep learning, which makes it relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and the application of these techniques in system integration (cs.SI), which are also relevant categories.
